Route O_TMPFILE and linkat(AT_EMPTY_PATH) through AgentOS host imports.

WASI Preview 1 cannot create or publish an unnamed inode. Reserve explicit
wasi-libc flag values and delegate those two operations to the managed runner,
which retains the descriptor until close and applies normal VFS hard-link
semantics when the inode is published.

